question: Will Sweden join NATO by April 30?
description:
This is a market on whether Sweden will officially join the North Atlantic Treaty Organization (NATO) as a full member state by April 30, 2023, 11:59:59 PM ET.

If Sweden has officially joined NATO as a full member state at any point by April 30, 2023, 11:59:59 PM ET this market will resolve as “Yes”. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No."

The primary settlement source for this market will be the official NATO website (https://www.nato.int/cps/en/natohq/nato_countries.htm), however other credible sources may be used.

events.title: Will Sweden join NATO by...?
events.description: This is a market group over by which date Sweden will have joined NATO.

question: Will Vox win over 45 seats in the 2023 Spanish general election?
description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if Vox gets over 45 seats in the Congress of Deputies (Congreso de los Diputados) in the 2023 Spanish general election scheduled for July 23. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

The primary resolution source for this market will be a consensus of credible reporting. In case of ambiguity official information from the Spanish government and/or information published through the official website of the Kingdom of Spain's Ministry of the Interior (https://infoelectoral.interior.gob.es/opencms/es/elecciones-celebradas/elecciones-anteriores/) will be used.

question: Will PP win a plurality in the 2023 Spanish general election?
description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if PP (Partido Popular, People's Party) controls a greater number of seats in the Congress of Deputies than any other party after the results of the 2023 Spanish general election are finalized. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

If the results of this election aren't known by December 31, 2023, 11:59:59 PM ET, this market will resolve to 50-50.

The primary resolution source for this market will be a consensus of credible reporting. question: Guatemala Presidential Election: Will Bernardo Arévalo win?
description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if Bernardo Arévalo wins the 2023 Guatemalan presidential election. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

This market includes any potential second round. If the result isn't known by December 31, 2023, 11:59:59 PM ET, the market will resolve to 50-50.

question: Rollbit rug by August 31?
description:
This market asks whether or not Rollbit, a well-known online cryptocurrency gambling platform, will undergo a 'rug pull' event by August 31, 2023. A 'rug pull' is a fraudulent practice in the world of cryptocurrency, where developers abandon a project and run away with investors' funds.

If Rollbit is reported to have executed a 'rug pull' in the form of sudden withdrawal of funds, abandonment of project, or otherwise shutting down with user funds still in their system by August 31, 2023, 11:59 PM ET, this market will resolve to "Yes". Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

The resolution of this market will be based on credible reports from trusted industry sources confirming the 'rug pull' event.

question: Arkham token above $1 one week after launch?
description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if Arkham token ($ARKM) is above $1.0000 (i.e. $1.0001 or greater) one week after launch. Otherwise, the market will resolve to "No."

"One week after launch" is defined as exactly 7 days (168 hours) after the token airdrop is claimable (see https://twitter.com/ArkhamIntel/status/1678422936427073536?s=20). This market description will be updated with the exact time of launch as soon as it is known.

The resolution source for this market will be Binance, specifically the spot price of $ARKM. If the price doesn't exist on Binance at resolution time, a consensus of highly liquid price sources will be used instead. If Arkham doesn't launch a token by December 31, 2023, 11:59 PM ET, this market will resolve to 50-50.

question: Will 'Mission: Impossible' gross over $100m on its 5-day open?
description:
This is a market on how much ‘Mission: Impossible - Dead Reckoning Part One' will gross domestically over its 5-day opening. The “Domestic Daily” tab on https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl1896449537/ be used to resolve this market once the values for the first five days of the film's release (July 12 - July 16) are final (i.e. not studio estimates).

This market will resolve to "Yes" if ‘Mission: Impossible - Dead Reckoning Part One’ grosses more than $100,000,000 on its 5-day opening. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

Please note, this market will resolve according to the sum of the Box Office Mojo numbers under Domestic Daily for July 12-16.

If there is no final data available by July 24, 2023, 11:59:59 PM ET, another credible resolution source will be chosen.

question: Will @realDonaldTrump tweet by July 31?
description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if @realDonaldTrump tweets at least once between July 9 and July 31, 11:59 PM ET. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

For the purposes of this market, all quote and reply tweets count toward a "Yes" resolution, but retweets will not count.

The resolution source for this market will be Donald J. Trump's verified Twitter account: https://twitter.com/realdonaldtrump.

Please note, only the @realDonaldTrump verified Twitter account counts for this market, regardless of the URL for this profile. If Donald J. Trump tweets from another account, it has no bearing on the resolution of this market.
